OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with bright
OL,6,Fspells but generally cloudier across
OL,7,FMoray and northern Aberdeenshire. Very
OL,8,Fwarm in the south with the best of the
OL,9,Fsunshine across southern Aberdeenshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly dry, bright and warm
OL,12,Fevening, with the best of the any late
OL,13,Fsunnier spells across southern
OL,14,FAberdeenshire. Remaining dry for the
OL,15,Frest of the night with clear spells.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA dry and settled day, albeit
OL,18,Ffeeling cooler compared to Monday
OL,19,Faround coasts. Plenty of sunshine in
OL,20,Fthe morning before more in the cloud
OL,21,Fdevelops into the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
